==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Æstivate
<hw>⟦AE⟧s"ti*vate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>aestivare</ets>, <ets>aestivatum</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
spend the summer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>To pass the summer in a state of
torpor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><altsp>[Spelt also <asp>estivate</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>AEstivation</ent>⟦br⟧
